T1  - The Path Goal Theory of Leader Effectiveness: An Operant Interpretation1
AU  - Mawhinney, Thomas C.
AU  - Ford, Jeffrey D.
Y1  - 1977/07/01
PY  - 1977
DA  - 1977/07/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1977.4281817
